videos.description: Virginia big man Mamadi Kiakite blocks a shot and Virginia goes the other way, moves the ball, and finds Kyle Guy for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Diakite block leads to Guy's 3-pointer

videos.description: Notre Dame guard TJ Gibbs launches a 3 from deep and knocks it down to cut Virginia's lead to 1.
videos.headline: Gibbs drains long 3-pointer
